Encode ← |2 (
  =2⊸type°□
  ⨬(□₂|⍥(/◇⊂≡⌟(□Encode⊙˜⊂)⊙"01")≠0⊸⧻)
  ⍆↯∞_2
)

Tree   ← °□⊣⊢⍢(⍆⊂⊂⊓/⍚+□°⊟⍉⇌⊃↙↘2|>1⧻)
Prep   ← ⍆⍉⊟≡⊓∘□∩⌞⊏⊸⍏⊕⊃⧻⊢⊸⊛
H      ← Encode ⊙"" Tree Prep
IsPref ← ≍∩⌞↙⊸⧻
Decode ← (
  °⊟⍉⊙⊙""
  ⍢(⟜₂((⊙⊂Flip⊙↘⊙⧻∩⌞(°□⊢▽))◡⋅≡⌟◇IsPref)|≠0⧻◌◌)
  ⋅⋅⋅⇌
)

Demo ← (
  ⊸H⊸(&p$"Original string: `_`\n-")
  ⊸≡(&p$"_ _"°⊟)&p"Huffman code:\n"
  ⟜(&p⊸$"\n-\nEncodes as: `_`"/◇⊂⊏⨂⊙Flip≡°□°⊟⍉)
  &p$"\n-\nWhich decodes as: `_`" Decode
)

Demo "this is an example for huffman encoding"
